<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 12:31:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储会议、七国集团政治动荡，债券动荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 11:16:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾向南海军事人员发送物资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-sends-provisions-military-personnel-south-china-sea-2024-12-17/</link><description>菲律宾表示，本月早些时候已向驻扎在马尼拉占领但北京声称拥有主权的南海岛礁上的军事人员提供了物资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 11:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-sends-provisions-military-personnel-south-china-sea-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>一名被称为中国特工的女子在针对英国军情五处的诉讼中败诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/woman-loses-case-against-uks-mi5-over-spy-alert-2024-12-17/</link><description>伦敦一家法庭周二裁定，一名被英国军情五处认定为中国间谍的女子因向政界人士发出警告称她是为北京工作的特工而起诉该国内间谍机构，但败诉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 10:28:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/woman-loses-case-against-uks-mi5-over-spy-alert-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>美银美林表示，投资者对美国股市的配置创历史新高，现金配置创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/investor-allocations-us-equities-record-high-cash-record-low-bofa-says-2024-12-17/</link><description>美国银行全球研究部 12 月的一项调查显示，本月投资者对美国股票的配置创下历史新高，欧洲股票、大宗商品和现金的配置有所下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 10:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/investor-allocations-us-equities-record-high-cash-record-low-bofa-says-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>印度黄金进口量继 11 月创纪录之后 12 月大幅下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-gold-imports-plunge-december-after-record-november-2024-12-17/</link><description>贸易和政府官员表示，在没有任何重大节日的情况下，以及价格反弹促使买家推迟购买，继 11 月份创纪录的购买量之后，印度的黄金进口预计在 12 月份将急剧放缓。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 09:34:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-gold-imports-plunge-december-after-record-november-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>外交部表示中方愿与印方通过边界谈判增进互信</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-ready-enhance-mutual-trust-with-india-border-talks-foreign-ministry-says-2024-12-17/</link><description>外交部周二表示，中方愿同印方一道，通过对话沟通增进互信，真诚管控分歧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 08:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-ready-enhance-mutual-trust-with-india-border-talks-foreign-ministry-says-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>巴西数字贷款机构 Nubank 向 Tyme Group 投资 1.5 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/brazilian-digital-lender-nubank-invests-150-million-tyme-group-2024-12-17/</link><description>巴西数字银行 Nubank 周一表示，已向 Tyme Group 投资 1.5 亿美元，Tyme Group 是一家总部位于新加坡的数字银行，由中国腾讯支持，在南非和菲律宾拥有 1500 万客户。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/brazilian-digital-lender-nubank-invests-150-million-tyme-group-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>随着新排放规则的临近，欧洲汽车制造商对电动汽车打折，提高汽油车价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europes-carmakers-discount-evs-hike-petrol-car-prices-new-emissions-rules-loom-2024-12-17/</link><description>欧洲汽车制造商正在提高汽油车的价格，并准备对电动汽车进行折扣，以迎接另一个挑战——更严格的排放规定，这可能会进一步缩减整个陷入困境的行业的利润。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 06:13:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europes-carmakers-discount-evs-hike-petrol-car-prices-new-emissions-rules-loom-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国与特朗普畅谈美中合作前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-trump-talk-up-prospects-us-china-collaboration-2024-12-17/</link><description>在特朗普重返白宫之前，两个超级大国已经阐明了各自的立场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 05:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-trump-talk-up-prospects-us-china-collaboration-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国计划到 2025 年将预算赤字占 GDP 的 4% 创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-plans-record-budget-deficit-4-gdp-2025-say-sources-2024-12-17/</link><description>消息人士称，中国领导人上周同意将预算赤字提高至有记录以来的最高水平，同时维持5%左右的经济增长目标。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 04:48:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-plans-record-budget-deficit-4-gdp-2025-say-sources-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴将亏损 13 亿美元出售中国百货连锁店银泰百货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/alibaba-sell-mall-chain-1-bln-part-latest-overhaul-2024-12-17/</link><description>阿里巴巴集团周二表示，将出售其中国百货商店子公司银泰百货，并因该交易损失 13 亿美元，因为这家零售巨头正在重组其业务组合，以专注于其核心电子商务业务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 04:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/alibaba-sell-mall-chain-1-bln-part-latest-overhaul-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>台北市长呼吁在中国官员罕见访华期间缓和紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taipei-mayor-calls-reduced-tensions-during-rare-visit-chinese-officials-2024-12-17/</link><description>台湾市长周二对来访的中国官员表示，他希望和平，希望岛内减少“船只和飞机的呼啸声”，并表示对话胜过对抗。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 03:28:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taipei-mayor-calls-reduced-tensions-during-rare-visit-chinese-officials-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国将过境免签停留期限延长至10天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-extends-visa-free-transit-stays-10-days-2024-12-17/</link><description>中国周二宣布放宽免签过境政策，将符合条件的外国游客的允许停留时间从原来的 72 至 144 小时延长至 240 小时，即 10 天，以吸引更多外国游客。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 03:03:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-extends-visa-free-transit-stays-10-days-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔玛与美团外卖公司联手提振中国电商销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/walmart-china-partners-with-chinese-delivery-giant-meituan-2024-12-17/</link><description>沃尔玛周二表示，它已与美团建立战略合作伙伴关系，根据该合作伙伴关系，这家中国公司已开始为沃尔玛商品提供送货服务，而这家美国公司将出现在其受欢迎的应用程序上。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 02:35:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/walmart-china-partners-with-chinese-delivery-giant-meituan-2024-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市波动，美元在央行会议前坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-17/</link><description>周二欧洲股市波动，而美元坚挺，交易员准备迎接本周一系列央行会议，美联储可能会降息，而日本央行目前则按兵不动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 02:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>